snippet.title: James Cameron's Dark Angel (PS2/Xbox Game) High Quality Trailer
snippet.description:
High quality trailer of the game James Cameron's Dark Angel, developed by Radical Entertainment and released in 2002 for PlayStation 2 and Xbox.

Source: Official Xbox Magazine (OXM) bonus DVD.
